<p align="justify">[dropcap]W[/dropcap]hether you need to get your company's design or logo out there, or looking for a way to sell your designs, our custom screen printing is the answer. We use plastisol inks in our custom screen printing‚Äîit contains no air-polluting solvents or volatile organic compounds. This type of screen printing does not have a plastic, heat transfer feel-it's a high quality screen print. You can rest assured that your screen printed towels are truly safe for¬†the environment right from the start. Our screen printing technique lasts a long time even after repeated washing.¬†We also offer digital printing, which allows us to print smaller runs with a large amount of detail, so whether you are looking to print one piece or 500 pieces, we can help you.</p>

